{"tid":1474041,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「明日大嶼」料在 6至9個月內 重新推出","createTime":"2019-08-15T04:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T05:15:25.000Z","uid":226548,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fccacfeb57886696d1f3b40fb4623628b2204767","tid":1474041,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190815/photo/bkn-20190815102824739-0815_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190815105956\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190815%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190815102824739-0815_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190815105956&h=120d1c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n08月15日(四) 10:28<br />\n<br />\n政府去年提出造價逾6000億港元的基建項目「明日大嶼」填海計劃，飽受各界批評。立法會建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界議員謝偉銓今早(15日)出席電台節目表示，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">在目前社會氣氛下，政府推出大型造地計劃會有阻延，相信「明日大嶼」要延遲半年至9個月。</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n他認為，為解市民燃眉之急，政府應先推出短期房屋措施，建議在未有急切需要作長遠用途的「鄉村式發展」用地，由政府主導興建過渡性房屋，避免用地因丁權案司法覆核而閒置。他又建議資助私人業主，透過改建工廈及在農地興建過渡性房屋，賣地時引入「只租不賣」私人住宅用地，提高及放寬九龍區地積比限制等。"},{"pid":"9cb08615bc90cd8992d6552b02bfed7e3120cf73","tid":1474041,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:44:54.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190815/mobile/bkn-20190815102824739-0815_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190815%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190815102824739-0815_00822_001.html&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=67ffdc5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190815/mobile/bkn-20190815102824739-0815_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f53ef5d1849159e3a1dc7cf4af13521401a066ec","tid":1474041,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"c76ccfa2494a412433782e2ffa7af4013100efeb","tid":1474041,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"必須停止<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"bf8dd670fa7625edb240f04497f6c5a8e792a68b","tid":1474041,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:03:59.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">818 手足要絕對和平！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依兩日trump/國際社會已經開哂口，關鍵時刻，咪掛住衝搞到外國幫唔到你口呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n就算出老解，你反抗都唔會有用，之前都傾好左，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">出老解係全人類返屋企！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n行前面既手足<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住幫幫手適當時拉住d激動手足</span></span>，唔洗理佢係咪鬼，總之睇撚住大家要冷静！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地主動出手既話外國點樣幫你口？？？？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你要贏老共緊係要引美帝打佢，自己掉磚邊會掉得贏；依家就係關鍵時刻，所以要冷静俾老美有位出手！！老美先係真正既勇武攬炒皇牌！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"f7f8f01b82443a595ce4586235e6f3f66e4e1043","tid":1474041,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:07:38.000Z","msg":"起呢個島真係當人水魚"},{"pid":"6aca27c586c2bbe4d045584fa81c24aa07349e27","tid":1474041,"uid":117276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:10:12.000Z","msg":"所以真係希望場運動可以頂到美國國會復會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時就有法案睇住支那<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ff4f45bd97c9af482f366bf71c385be4d7c9b1","tid":1474041,"uid":274680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:11:35.000Z","msg":"睇來共產黨真係好等錢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj